 ## r1
 
 Adds discovery and binding for the existing DbApiSqlContextStore surface.
+
+## r5
+
+Adapts the Scheduler-managed wrapper to call existing `upsert_record` methods
+with a record-like object when the existing store rejects a raw payload dict.
+This keeps the real `DbApiSqlContextStore` contract intact and still returns a
+`sql_ref` derived from the record `context_ref`.
